## ğŸ³ Docker Usage

### Individual Agent Containers
```bash
# Build agent container
cd agents/{{agents.0.id}}
docker build -t {{theme}}-{{agents.0.id}} .

# Run agent container
docker run -p {{agents.0.ports.backend}}:{{agents.0.ports.backend}} -p {{agents.0.ports.frontend}}:{{agents.0.ports.frontend}} {{theme}}-{{agents.0.id}}
```

### Docker Compose (All Agents)
```bash
# Start all agents with Docker Compose
cd docker
docker-compose -f docker-compose.{{theme}}.yml up -d

# View logs
docker-compose -f docker-compose.{{theme}}.yml logs -f

# Stop all agents
docker-compose -f docker-compose.{{theme}}.yml down
```

